    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the patties are almost cooked, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>from the oven and top each patty with a<strong> cheese flavour slice</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and add them to the other side of the tray</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for 3-4 min or until the cheese has melted and the ciabatta halves are warmed through</p>",
