        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill each <strong>warmed ciabatta</strong> with a <strong>lettuce leaf </strong>and a <strong>cheezy vegan patty, </strong>then top<strong> </strong>the patty with the <strong>black</strong> <strong>bean chilli </strong>and the<strong> quick-pickled chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – these are your <strong>plant-based chilli cheezeburgers</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>smoky fries</strong> and<strong> lettuce wedges</strong> to the side and drizzle some of the <strong>pickling liquid</strong> over the lettuce</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
